<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>When was the last time you pulled a mob, I was the main puller for my guild all the way through ToV until they nerfed Eye of Zomm.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
