<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>PBAE? Quad Kiting? Roots? Snares? Stuns? Rains? Lures?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
Again, lots of stuff being sited as broken without a single example. PBAE still works just fine. It has limited use 61+ but it still has its place and it is still a great way to exp up to 60. With the mob level exp change it might even be a good way to exp post 61 as well.<br>
<br>
Quad kiting still works just as well as it did in beta. Sure some places where dicked with, but with good reason. There are still dozens of quaddable zones and it still remains one of the best ways to get exp and certainly the best solo exp bar none.<br>
<br>
Roots? Snares? Maybe I missed the nerf here. How have any of these spells changed?<br>
<br>
Rains? Lures? These spells still work great as well. Now that we understand how rains work we have been able to use them more effectively. We even got rain upgrades that are great spells and do great damage. Same with Lures, we got some very good damage, basically unresistable spells. With modern mana regen due to buffs and gear, the 60+ lures are a very good choice when you have to do damage fast and reliably. They are basically guaranteed to land for full when you absolutely have to do damage and resists could be catastrophic.<br>
<br>
So please enlighten me as to all the nerfs that have killed our class so much that we are the top raid, group, and solo damage in the game. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=natanmagus>Natan Magus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1019<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/11/03 4:34 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re:</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>So please enlighten me as to all the nerfs that have killed our class so much that we are the top raid, group, and solo damage in the game.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
